  <brief_title>Prospective Study of Head and Neck Cancer Radiation Treatment With or Without Amifostine</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Open-label, Randomized, Control Study of Head and Neck Cancer Radiation Treatment With or Without Amifostine</official_title>
